of another school.

173
00:12:38.090 --> 00:12:39.757
He won't get into college.

174
00:12:39.792 --> 00:12:40.824
Thank you for coming.

175
00:12:40.860 --> 00:12:42.092
Helen.

176
00:12:42.128 --> 00:12:43.927
