next week.

179
00:12:50.369 --> 00:12:52.903
I think you should be there too.

180
00:12:52.938 --> 00:12:54.938
When is it?

181
00:12:56.542 --> 00:12:58.542
It's thursday at four.

182
00:12:59.745 --> 00:13:01.211
Okay. I'll try.

183
00:13:07.787 --> 00:13:09.286
Let's go. mom.

184
00:13:09.321 --> 00:13:12.856
Martin. come and say good-bye
to your father.

185
00:13:12.892 --> 00:13:14.124
Martin. did you hear me?

186
00:13:14.160 --> 00:13:15.893
I said. "come and say
good-bye to your... ".

187
00:13:15.928 --> 00:13:17.895
Don't make him. helen. Please.

188
