You have a lovely home.

189
00:13:50.930 --> 00:13:52.062
Thank you.

190
00:13:52.098 --> 00:13:54.431
It's not mine.

191
00:13:54.467 --> 00:13:57.501
You're not the husband?

192
00:13:57.536 --> 00:13:59.770
