nina's husband.

194
00:14:01.774 --> 00:14:03.807
No. no. no. I'm the brother.

195
00:14:03.843 --> 00:14:06.477
The brother.

196
00:14:06.512 --> 00:14:08.679
The brother who went to prison?

197
00:14:10.649 --> 00:14:12.616
You killed him. you know.

198
00:14:12.651 --> 00:14:14.952
With your antics.

199
00:14:14.987 --> 00:14:18.155
He died of a broken heart.

200
00:14:18.190 --> 00:14:19.990
I thought he died of emphysema.

201
00:14:20.025 --> 00:14:22.092
You're a horror.

202
00:14:22.128 --> 00:14:23.994
Excuse me. donna.

203
00:14:24.029 --> 00:14:26.597
I hope you don't mind terribly.
I'm gonna steal my brother.

204
00:14:26.632 --> 00:14:28.098
Where you going?

205
00:14:28.134 --> 00:14:31.101
To grieve.

206
00:14:31.137 --> 00:14:32.137
Come on.

207
00:14:37.376 --> 00:14:38.376
Here.

208
00:14:50.489 --> 00:14:52.489
Muscle relaxants.

209
00:15:04.370 --> 00:15:06.470
