288
00:20:15.481 --> 00:20:18.148
We needed it.

289
00:20:18.183 --> 00:20:21.318
Fuck it.

290
00:20:25.891 --> 00:20:26.790
Here. let me.

291
00:20:26.825 --> 00:20:28.658
No. I got it.

292
00:20:28.694 --> 00:20:30.560
I got it.

293
