793
00:47:46.497 --> 00:47:47.896
Yes.

794
00:47:49.299 --> 00:47:50.265
I like it.

795
00:47:50.300 --> 00:47:51.666
I like it too.

796
00:47:51.702 --> 00:47:52.667
It smells familiar.

797
00:47:52.703 --> 00:47:53.969
I don't know what it is.

798
00:47:54.004 --> 00:47:56.805
It reminds me of home.

799
00:47:56.840 --> 00:48:00.308
Were you offended by
the conversation downstairs?

800
00:48:00.344 --> 00:48:02.677
Nah. of course not.

801
00:48:02.713 --> 00:48:06.148
They're all entitled to
their... Opinions.

802
00:48:06.183 --> 00:48:07.449
They're young.

803
00:48:07.484 --> 00:48:10.118
They want everything to be
black and white.

804
00:48:10.154 --> 00:48:13.155
And the tragedy is.
you can't move them beyond that.

805
00:48:13.190 --> 00:48:14.790
No matter how much.

806
00:48:14.825 --> 00:48:17.159
You tell them. no matter
how many books they read.

807
00:48:17.194 --> 00:48:19.694
There are just some things
that can't be taught.

808
00:48:19.730 --> 00:48:22.964
Things like humility and loss.

809
00:48:23.000 --> 00:48:25.367
And desire.

810
00:48:29.106 --> 00:48:31.006
I loved your book.

811
00:48:34.211 --> 00:48:35.677
Thank you.

812
00:48:35.712 --> 00:48:37.746
Is there going to be
another one?

813
00:48:37.781 --> 00:48:39.181
I hope so. eventually.

814
00:48:39.216 --> 00:48:41.016
About the same people?

815
00:48:41.051 --> 00:48:44.820
No. no. No. i...

816
00:48:44.855 --> 00:48:46.488
I mean. it's an old book.

817
00:48:46.523 --> 00:48:48.089
You know?

818
00:48:48.125 --> 00:48:50.158
I'm not writing
that kind of thing anymore.

819
00:48:50.194 --> 00:48:51.693
Why not?

820
00:48:51.728 --> 00:48:54.262
Why. it's... i'm just...

821
00:48:54.298 --> 00:48:55.897
Tell you the truth.
I don't really.

822
00:48:55.933 --> 00:48:57.499
Recognize that author.

823
00:48:59.303 --> 00:49:01.603
People change.

824
00:49:01.638 --> 00:49:02.604
Yeah.

825
00:49:02.639 --> 00:49:03.605
Lucky for you.

826
00:49:03.640 --> 00:49:05.006
You have a paper record.

827
00:49:05.042 --> 00:49:07.142
Of the man you used to be.

828
00:49:09.379 --> 00:49:11.546
Whereas for most of us
that younger person only exists.

829
00:49:11.582 --> 00:49:13.582
In our memory.

830
00:49:17.955 --> 00:49:19.955
I'm glad you're here.

831
00:49:27.297 --> 00:49:30.265
I was beginning to think.

832
00:49:30.300 --> 00:49:34.302
There wasn't anyone interesting
to talk to in all of new jersey.

833
00:49:37.274 --> 00:49:42.244
But... You're a famous author.

834
00:49:48.585 --> 00:49:51.753
And you've been to prison.

835
00:49:57.794 --> 00:50:01.096
<i>Sir thomas malory wrote
le morte d'arthur.</i>

836
00:50:01.131 --> 00:50:05.000
When he was prison.
Did you know that?

837
00:50:05.035 --> 00:50:08.236
No. I didn't.

838
00:50:10.674 --> 00:50:13.308
So you're in good company.

839
00:50:13.343 --> 00:50:16.745
Though many scholars believe
that the charges...

840
00:50:19.149 --> 00:50:22.984
Levied against him...

841
00:50:23.020 --> 00:50:25.754
Were invented.

842
00:50:43.807 --> 00:50:45.607
What's wrong?

843
00:50:51.248 --> 00:50:52.981
I-I don't feel...
I don't feel well.

844
00:50:53.016 --> 00:50:53.815
All of a sudden.

845
00:50:53.850 --> 00:50:54.716
Sit. sit.

846
00:50:54.751 --> 00:50:56.751
No. it's okay.

847
00:50:57.854 --> 00:51:00.221
I-I'll show myself out.

848
00:53:18.462 --> 00:53:21.863
<i>Hi. you've reached
the voicemail of alison and...</i>

849
00:53:21.898 --> 00:53:23.098
<i>joanie. We can't get to.</i>

850
00:53:23.133 --> 00:53:24.165
<i>The phone right now.</i>

851
00:53:24.201 --> 00:53:25.800
<i>So just leave us a message.</i>

852
00:53:25.836 --> 00:53:27.469
<i>And we'll get back
as soon as we can.</i>

853
00:53:27.504 --> 00:53:29.337
<i>Thank you. and have a great day.</i>

854
00:53:31.007 --> 00:53:32.774
Hey. it's me. Um...

855
00:53:35.412 --> 00:53:38.546
I know you told me not to
contact you. but...

856
00:53:40.484 --> 00:53:42.617
But I. um...

857
00:53:42.652 --> 00:53:45.620
I just needed to
hear your voice. so...

858
00:53:50.660 --> 00:53:52.827
And now I have. so...

859
00:53:52.863 --> 00:53:54.562
So...
